      <title>ASML 邁向荷蘭埃因霍溫的大規模擴張</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/asml-opts-expand-eindhoven-netherlands-2024-04-22/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[電腦晶片製造商最大的設備供應商阿斯麥 (ASML) 正在考慮在荷蘭埃因霍溫市進行大規模擴張，這是解決其未來業務拓展地點疑慮的重要一步。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/technology/asml-opts-expand-eindhoven-netherlands-2024-04-22/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 12:56:54 GMT</pubDate>
